examples.en: You ought not to give way to your temper, under whatever provocation.
He was accused of deliberate provocation.
He can turn violent at the least provocation.
She claims that Graham attacked her without any provocation.
With hardly any provocation, the crowd began to chant.
Julie has a tendency to burst into tears at the slightest provocation.
Her calmness in the face of repeated provocations impressed her friends.
